        <mj-text align="center" font-size="40px" color="grey" font-family="Helvetica Neue" font-weight="200"><h1>Markdown parser for MJLM templates</h1>

<p>This is a MarkDown parser that transforms into html by the use of mjml as a jinja template</p></mj-text>
        <mj-divider horizontal-spacing="0" vertical-spacing="0" padding-top="20" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" padding-right="0px" border-width="1px" border-color="#f8f8f8"></mj-divider>
